    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## ⚠️ Error Handling\nIf any node in this workflow fails, the error is automatically caught and forwarded to the Error Logger workflow. It logs the failure details into Google Sheets, where the KPI tracker dashboard displays the live error count.",
